data.title: Land & Agribusiness
data.meta_description: The Kidder Mathews land & agribusiness group brings deep commercial real estate and local market expertise to assist in the sale and lease of commercial land and agribusiness properties.  We represent a diverse clientele including developers, institutional, and private buyers and sellers for this asset class.
data.text:
The Kidder Mathews Land & Agribusiness group brings deep commercial real estate combined with regional and local market expertise to assist in the sale and lease of commercial land, agricultural land, and agricultural properties. We represent a diverse clientele, including developers, institutional and corporate clients, investment trusts, and private buyers and sellers for this asset class.

Our Land & Agribusiness Advisory specialists are dedicated to achieving client goals and completing successful transactions on your behalf. In the past two years, Kidder Mathews has assisted clients with over $4.3 billion in land deals, representing over 400,000 acres.
